sources.title: Men with Steel Faces (1940) Gene Autry | Adventure, Music, Sci-Fi | Full Length Movie
sources.description:
When Danger Threatened HELP CAME FROM THE SKIES! 
Singer Gene Autry discovers a race of advanced humans living beneath the earth. 

Re-edited feature version of serial The Phantom Empire (1935). 

Directors: Otto Brower, B. Reeves Eason
Writers: Hy Freedman, Gerald Geraghty, Wallace MacDonald
Stars: Gene Autry, Frankie Darro, Smiley Burnette
